    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add your <strong>fine egg noodles</strong> to a large bowl, cover them with <strong>boiled water</strong> until fully submerged and stir for 10 sec until the noodles separate</p><p>Set aside to soak for 4 min, or until softened</p><p>Once softened, drain the noodles, run them under <strong>cold water</strong> for 10 sec until slightly cooled, then set aside to drain further</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2198.-step-3-x200.jpg",
