      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Rip the outer leaves of your<strong> lettuce[s]</strong> into large, bite-sized pieces then shred the <strong>inner core</strong></p><p>Strip your <strong>mint leaves</strong> from their stalks and chop them roughly, discarding the stalks</p><p>Chop your <strong>coriander</strong> finely, including the stalks</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
