            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> ripped lettuce</strong>, <strong>drained noodles</strong>, <strong>chopped mango</strong> and most of the <strong>chopped chilli</strong> (not a fan of spice? Just add a little!) to a bowl with the <strong>dressing</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>noodle salad</strong></p><p>Transfer the<strong> crispy chicken</strong> to a clean board and shred apart into roughly bite-sized pieces using two forks – this technique is known as 'pulling'</p>",
      "order": 7,
