      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>noodle salad</strong> topped with the <strong>crispy chicken</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>chopped herbs</strong> and <strong>remaining chopped chilli</strong> (remember to go easy if you don’t like spice)</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
